Package: scGSVA
Type: Package
Title: GSVA and UCell signature enrichment analysis for single cell RNA seq
Version: 0.0.25
Authors@R: c(person("Kai","Guo",email = "guokai8@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")
          ),
          person("Zhihan","Wang",role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Kai Guo <guokai8@gmail.com>
Description: scGSVA provides functions to perform GSVA, ssGSEA, and UCell
    enrichment analysis for single-cell RNA-seq data. The package includes
    functions to build gene set annotations for multiple species (KEGG, GO,
    MSigDB) and generate publication-ready visualizations.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
